timeOut: Experience Content could not be retrieved for one or more analysis cases.
timeOutCause1: Internet Explorer cannot handle amount of received data.
timeOutCause2: Experience Content is too large for current browser.
invalid: analysis cases have an empty or invalid Experience Content.
invalid1: analysis case has an empty or invalid Experience Content.
filteredContent: Simulation Experience Content is limited to 3D animation in this App. Other elements like charts can be displayed in Physics Simulation Review (V+R).
partialFiltered: content filtered as they can only be displayed in Physics Simulation Review (V+R).
partialFiltered1: content filtered as it can only be displayed in Physics Simulation Review (V+R).
